YD Bio Limited (Nasdaq: YDES) is a biotechnology company dedicated to precision medicine and innovative diagnostics.
At this year’s medical technology exhibition, we will highlight three key areas shaping the future of oncology:
(1) Early Cancer Detection – Non-invasive cancer tests based on DNA methylation and multi-biomarker technologies for breast, pancreatic, colorectal and other cancers, including licensed pancreatic and breast cancer tests from EG BioMed to help identify high-risk patients earlier;
(2) Innovative Health Diagnostics – Replacing one-size-fits-all medicine with next-generation precision diagnostics that use finer stratification and individualized analysis to support faster and more accurate treatment decisions;
(3) Advanced Cell Therapies & Exosome-Based Therapeutics – Combining stem cell and exosome technologies to repair and protect ophthalmic and related diseases, enabling a new generation of eye-care solutions.
We are not just a single company, but an integrated biomedical value chain connecting research, clinical application, and industrialization—so that innovation can move beyond the lab and reach patients more rapidly and effectively.
